{"tid":411561,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術研究]點解企係到會攰過行路？","createTime":"2017-09-24T02:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T03:46:34.000Z","uid":18821,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2dd96d79228aab0b49323e29778da20660d2861","tid":411561,"uid":18821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"相信大家都試過企係到等人/罰企etc 點解企係到唔郁永遠都攰過行同等時間嘅路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6656a8820eb5471fe659452ddbe24fec8cda71ca","tid":411561,"uid":18821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"同埋行路係輪流用一隻腳去支撐成個身體，相反企就2隻腳平分如果係正常姿勢，點解都係企係到對腳會攰啲？"},{"pid":"f2a4a2c312ed40db9fb8e1cd67651815b87d696e","tid":411561,"uid":18821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fc95cbce4bbf3ba3f372783b46426df2584dd3","tid":411561,"uid":18821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4639803a1a83795bcfffce5a88a58e50caf06d3a","tid":411561,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:18:51.000Z","msg":"因為一路用同一組肌肉（？）"},{"pid":"3c01f0e488660ad0d43e256c0269563974a0f393","tid":411561,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"行路用10舊肌肉攰啲？ 定企用一舊肌肉攰啲？"},{"pid":"888a4d0f2ef2b5ae27f1dab31e45697a021b985e","tid":411561,"uid":15336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"行路用既肌肉多啲 分擔左個工作<br />\n同埋行路左右腳可以輪替休息<br />\n但企定定就逼肌肉長時間工作"},{"pid":"a8d223fc312a9255278f4f862bdc0c8445d4e9dc","tid":411561,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:34:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋行路係輪流用一隻腳去支撐成個身體，相反企就2隻腳平分如果係正常姿勢，點解都係企係到對腳會攰啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果用腳既數量黎計，千足蟲咪唔識攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好單從睇腳數量咁'乎'淺，人進化出黎既腳係夠支撐身體。細分啲睇肌肉，企係度長時間用死一舊肌肉，邊個都攰啦。行路咁多舊肌肉輪流運作，自然無咁攰"},{"pid":"07a69b88b791106fbf2231503d761d67ad42fb17","tid":411561,"uid":3852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:41:09.000Z","msg":"心理都有影響？<br />\n企響度多數係等人/等車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自然唔耐煩"},{"pid":"e86d0f0e9c2009ba3ba85cd80b3e67b69bd5686a","tid":411561,"uid":18821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"巴打們好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇諗過肌肉個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c1300818101e9781026c64f41d5cfcc4a62c61","tid":411561,"uid":51357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:35:00.000Z","msg":"成日企到骨痛又係點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528b3463c4eb6dab09f796d246a893a61ee063a3","tid":411561,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打們好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇諗過肌肉個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係你on9,講攰唔諗肌肉唔通諗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n定你想講精神上攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"8dc1afb9388b99314171793d719ca3ec50730d9c","tid":411561,"uid":111957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:44:01.000Z","msg":"點解陪條女行街一個鐘仲攰過打波幾粒鐘<img sr